{"tid":1171499,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〔德國難民法〕濫捕、政治檢控同屬政治迫害　政府講司法獨立只係轉移視線","createTime":"2019-05-25T17:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T23:25:55.000Z","uid":127728,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9449d57da1bb0f4d0991f42abd915db02ad977a2","tid":1171499,"uid":127728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T17:51:38.000Z","msg":"林鄭同葉劉話德國批難民庇護係衝擊香港司法獨立，根本係轉移視線。睇返德國基本法同難民法，選擇性拘捕同檢控都屬於政治迫害嘅一種，受害人應獲得難民保護。<br />\n<br />\n以下嘅野，好多巴絲打都已經講過，我只係整合返啲資料，當做個存照。<br />\n<br />\n仔細睇返德國聯邦移民及難民局2018年5月，即係黃台仰同李東昇獲批難民保護時嘅統計數據（第4頁）：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bamf.de/SharedDocs/Anlagen/DE/Downloads/Infothek/Statistik/Asyl/hkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-mai-2018.pdf?__blob=publicationFile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bamf.de%2FSharedDocs%2FAnlagen%2FDE%2FDownloads%2FInfothek%2FStatistik%2FAsyl%2Fhkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-mai-2018.pdf%3F__blob%3DpublicationFile&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFImB5A%2F6U2CfHiGB6dLXW7A%3D&h=6955c335\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bamf.de/SharedDocs/Anlagen/DE/Downloads/Infothek/Statistik/Asyl/hkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-mai-2018.pdf?__blob=publicationFile</a><br />\n<br />\n兩個香港人係根據德國難民法第3部 第1條 (Anerkennungen als Fl&uuml;chtlinggem. &sect; 3 I AsylG) 獲得難民保護，難民法第3部 第1條就係講一個人如果因為國籍、政見、所屬團體等理由受到迫害就符合難民定義。咁咩係「迫害」呢？原來第3a部 第2條寫得好清楚：<br />\n<br />\nActs of persecution<br />\n<br />\n(2) Acts of persecution as referred to in subsection 1 may among others take the form of:<br />\n1.  acts of physical or mental violence, including acts of sexual violence;<br />\n<br />\n2.  <span style=\"color: red;\">legal, administrative, police or judicial measures which are in themselves discriminatory or which are implemented in a discriminatory manner</span>;<br />\n<br />\n3.  <span style=\"color: red;\">disproportionate or discriminatory prosecution or punishment</span>;<br />\n<br />\n4.  denial of judicial redress resulting in a disproportionate or discriminatory punishment;<br />\n<br />\n5.  prosecution or punishment for refusal to perform military service in a conflict, where performing military service would include crimes or acts falling under the exclusion clauses as set out in Section 3(2);<br />\n<br />\n6.  acts which are of a gender-specific nature or are directed against children.<br />\n<br />\n咁即係話「迫害」唔一定係因為司法唔獨立（雖然有幾獨立大家有目共睹），亦可以由檢控、行政、或者執法當局進行，亦包括選擇性或者不合比例嘅檢控或者判罰。一同被控暴動罪嘅梁天琦係喺2018年5月18日由陪審團判罪名成立，6月11日被重判，<span style=\"color: red;\">即係德國5月批出難民保護嘅原因好大可能係基於政治檢控</span>。<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，第3a部 第1條亦指出當局必須要係嚴重地，或者長時間不斷地侵犯基本人權，德國先至會視之為「迫害」，即係德國已經觀察左一段長時間先會得出香港政府致治迫害抗爭者呢個結論。<br />\n<br />\n(1) Acts of persecution within the meaning of Section 3 (1) must<br />\n<br />\n1.  be sufficiently serious by their nature or repetition as to constitute a severe violation of basic human rights, in particular the rights from which derogation cannot be made under Article 15 (2) of the European Convention for the Protection of Human Rights and Fundamental Freedoms; or<br />\n<br />\n2.  be an accumulation of various measures, including violations of human rights which is sufficiently severe as to affect an individual in a similar manner as mentioned in no. 1.<br />\n<br />\n再睇埋難民法第3部 第2條 第2款：<br />\n<br />\n(2) A foreigner shall not qualify as a refugee under subsection 1 where there are serious reasons to believe that he<br />\n1.  has committed a crime against peace, a war crime or a crime against humanity within the meaning of the international instruments drawn up for the purpose of establishing provisions regarding such crimes,<br />\n<br />\n2.  <span style=\"color: red;\">committed a serious non-political crime outside the federal territory before being admitted as a refugee</span>, in particular a brutal act, even if it was supposedly intended to pursue political aims, or<br />\n<br />\n3.  acted in violation of the aims and principles of the United Nations.<br />\n<br />\n換言之，如果德國有理由認為黃台仰李東昇曾經犯過，或者煽惑他人參與嚴重嘅「非政治」罪行，係冇可能批出難民保護。德國基本上確認左檢控暴動罪呢個行為係帶有政治性質嘅迫害行為。<br />\n<br />\n德國難民法第3部 <a href=\"https://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/asylvfg_1992/__3.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gesetze-im-internet.de%2Fasylvfg_1992%2F__3.html&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFImB5A%2F6U2CfHiGB6dLXW7A%3D&h=026f1cc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/asylvfg_1992/__3.html</a><br />\n官方英文翻譯 <a href=\"http://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/englisch_asylvfg/englisch_asylvfg.html#p0029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gesetze-im-internet.de%2Fenglisch_asylvfg%2Fenglisch_asylvfg.html%23p0029&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFImB5A%2F6U2CfHiGB6dLXW7A%3D&h=cac7910b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/englisch_asylvfg/englisch_asylvfg.html#p0029</a><br />\n<br />\n德國基本法第16a條 <a href=\"http://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/gg/art_16a.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gesetze-im-internet.de%2Fgg%2Fart_16a.html&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFImB5A%2F6U2CfHiGB6dLXW7A%3D&h=66ffffcd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/gg/art_16a.html</a><br />\n官方英文翻譯 <a href=\"http://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/englisch_gg/englisch_gg.html#p0095\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gesetze-im-internet.de%2Fenglisch_gg%2Fenglisch_gg.html%23p0095&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFImB5A%2F6U2CfHiGB6dLXW7A%3D&h=28806a86\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/englisch_gg/englisch_gg.html#p0095</a>"},{"pid":"812dc6ccb6cb4e955345eefe9318a57aae101b5c","tid":1171499,"uid":91721,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T17:52:58.000Z","msg":"香港都要出政治犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e421d7e89b42b8f46e40cd791088e00e55c18ff0","tid":1171499,"uid":127728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T17:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse