000Z","msg":"梁天琦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T18:09:49.000Z","msg":"其實等同宣布埋天琦係政治犯，支共先咁緊張一味話破壞法治，司法獨立云云<br />\n<br />\n上年判天琦果個法官應該都無晒面見人"},{"pid":"c897e6f6aa9073c7ff3faf1a19f42a3b39a58c13","tid":1171499,"uid":78791,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T18:10:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c1504e0ac4f25284a2e395f123ee83e17d99883","tid":1171499,"uid":127728,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"c897e6f6aa9073c7ff3faf1a19f42a3b39a58c13","tid":1171499,"uid":78791,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T18:10:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T18:21:13.000Z","msg":"簡單黎講即係德國好大可能係基於律政師政治檢控先批出難民保護，亦確認左兩位實際上並冇犯到任何非政治性質嘅嚴重罪行。<br />\n777政權近日講司法獨立根本唔係重點，濫捕同政治檢控先係德國眼中「政治迫害」嘅行為。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6de36009397d79444b3f8e1439a2508460486c1","tid":1171499,"uid":143033,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T18:47:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4d6fcd11f8d76911df3dae8aae9d8f08d7271fa","tid":1171499,"uid":127728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T20:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280c225ebe7ffb3250ad4cd4b0a97d3a21aa6a5f","tid":1171499,"uid":5627,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T20:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UNsHgKK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUNsHgKK.jpg&h=95297bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqNoLC4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqNoLC4.png&h=0c0665ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"684e2708ade19370181c02e2d787e3ab25b224ea","tid":1171499,"uid